1. Female, RV (MP-O-1692, holotype). 2. Female, LV (MP-O-1694). 3. Female, dorsal view (MP-O-1695). 4. Male, RV (MP-O-1693). 5. Male, LV (MP-O-1693). 6. Central muscle scars, RV (MP-O- 1696). 7. Hinge (MP-O-1697). 8. Sieve-type normal pore canal (MP-O-1692, holotype). 9. Lip-type normal pore canal (MP-O- 1692, holotype). 10. 
<taxonomicName box="[362,487,1977,1999]" class="Ostracoda" family="Xestoleberididae" genus="Xestoleberis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Podocopida" pageId="13" pageNumber="190" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
